WEBVTT

00:11:59.280 --> 00:12:02.896
expressing wants, needs and desires,

00:12:02.920 --> 00:12:06.056
or hearing those of others
by really listening.

00:12:06.080 --> 00:12:09.416
All this is how the world
knows who we are.

00:12:09.440 --> 00:12:11.240
So who are we without it?

00:12:12.480 --> 00:12:15.656
True communication increases understanding

00:12:15.680 --> 00:12:18.720
and creates a more caring
and compassionate world.

00:12:19.800 --> 00:12:22.896
Once, I was perceived
to be an inanimate object,

00:12:22.920 --> 00:12:26.216
a mindless phantom
of a boy in a wheelchair.

00:12:26.240 --> 00:12:28.496
Today, I am so much more.

00:12:28.520 --> 00:12:30.936
A husband, a son, a friend,